§§ `The mandatory possession order fires when the ground is made out`

-- When the ground is made out the residual obligation is the Court's duty to
-- order possession; performing it within the window discharges (FULFILLED).
#TRACE `ground 7A possession order` `claim via Condition 1` AT 0 WITH
    PARTY Court DOES `order possession` AT 10

-- When the ground is not made out the contract is immediately FULFILLED.
#TRACE `ground 7A possession order` `base — nothing met` AT 0 WITH
    PARTY Court DOES `order possession` AT 10
